            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit"></span></div></div></div><p>另外还有亚历山大·麦考尔·史密斯的《间谍的私生活和报仇的精致艺术》和乔纳森·佩恩的《公民奥尔洛夫》。<em>汤姆·诺兰评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/mysteries-the-man-in-the-corduroy-suit-by-james-wolff-da935352?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/schoenberg-review-hard-to-like-impossible-to-ignore-99e96580?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《勋伯格》评论：难以喜欢，无法忽视</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/schoenberg-review-hard-to-like-impossible-to-ignore-99e96580"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-820656?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">史密斯档案馆/阿拉米</span></div></div></div><p>这位作曲家根据革命性的思想创作了尖锐、困难的音乐。欣赏它的力量需要练习。<em>蒂姆·佩奇的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/schoenberg-review-hard-to-like-impossible-to-ignore-99e96580?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
